  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a developmental protocol to determine the MRI based 31P-MRS changes seen in subjects
      with mitochondrial myopathy using our dynamic exercise protocol and to identify the ideal
      variable(s) to represent mitochondrial function.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
